info.description:
Desktop Client for the LEAP Platform.
LEAP (LEAP Encryption Access Project) develops a multi-year plan to secure everyday communication, breaking downinto discrete services, to be rolled out one at a time.
The client for the current phase gives support to the EIP Service.EIP (the Encrypted Internet Proxy) provides circumvention, location anonymization, and traffic encryption in a hassle-free, automatically self-configuring fashion, and has an enhanced level of security.
